https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/twx3c3SYYvpkuKOpZ57yfodNr0f.jpg The Cyrano Agency is a dating agency which helps people who can't date to have a love life. The agency staff try helping their clients without being noticed. The agency's representatives Byeong-hoon and Min-yeong are giving their best to pair up their client, Sang-yong, with his love interest named Hee-joong.
